OL,3,C'It was horrific': UK hair transplant
OL,4,Cpatients left disfigured and scarred
OL,6,FHair transplant patients have been
OL,7,Fleft disfigured and with extensive
OL,8,Fscarring following an increasing
OL,9,Fnumber of 'black market' treatments in
OL,10,Fthe UK, according to the industry body.
OL,12,FIt has prompted the British
OL,13,FAssociation of Hair Restoration
OL,14,FSurgery (BAHRS) to call for better
OL,15,Fregulation of the sector, including a
OL,16,Frequirement that only licensed medical
OL,17,Fdoctors carry out the procedure.
