OL,3,C'It was horrific': UK hair transplant
OL,4,Cpatients left disfigured and scarred
OL,6,F"I didn't trust the Turkish clinics,
OL,7,Fso decided to stay in the UK," the
OL,8,Fman, who wanted to remain anonymous,
OL,9,Fsaid.
OL,11,F"However, my experience was extremely
OL,12,Fpoor, and I know that some of the
OL,13,Fincisions were made by non-doctors.
OL,15,F"The results were very disappointing.
OL,17,F"My head was sore for at least two
OL,18,Fmonths afterwards."
