OL,3,C'It was horrific': UK hair transplant
OL,4,Cpatients left disfigured and scarred
OL,6,FThe BAHRS said the man's experience
OL,7,Fwas far from unique and many people
OL,8,Fhave had to undergo restorative
OL,9,Fprocedures to fix damage with a
OL,10,Fproperly trained surgeon.
OL,12,FHair transplant surgeon Greg Williams,
OL,13,Fwho is the BAHRS vice president, said
OL,14,Fit was crucial that Follicular Unit
OL,15,FExcisions (FUE) - which involve
OL,16,Fharvesting hair from the back and
OL,17,Fsides of the head and grafting it into
OL,18,Ftiny cuts made to balding areas of the
OL,19,Fscalp - were carried out by licensed
OL,20,Fand qualified doctors.
