OL,11,F"There is a problematic rise in
OL,12,Funlicensed technicians being allowed
OL,13,Fto perform the skin incision step
OL,14,Frather than just the graft extraction
OL,15,Fstep," he said.
OL,17,F"The decisions involved in harvesting
OL,18,Ffollicular units rely on the knowledge
OL,19,Fand experience of the hair transplant
OL,20,Fsurgeon and requires judgement.
