OL,6,F"It is not just a simple technical
OL,7,Fskill."
OL,9,FThe BAHRS says there were many
OL,10,Freputable and qualified providers in
OL,11,Fthe UK, but warned patients against
OL,12,Fmaking "poorly researched" decisions.
OL,14,FA Brighton man says he wished he had
OL,15,Fdone more research after finding his
OL,16,Fclinic through an advert on Facebook
OL,17,Fwhich offered hair transplant surgery
OL,18,Ffor #2,000.
