OL,6,F"With my first surgery, the incisions
OL,7,Ffelt like and made the same noise as a
OL,8,Ffork going into polystyrene," he said.
OL,10,F"It was horrific.
OL,12,F"I had pain and discomfort for six to
OL,13,F12 months.
OL,15,F"I was left with deep head scarring,
OL,16,Flong term pain and psychological
OL,17,Fdamage after 'black market' hair
OL,18,Ftransplant surgery."
